<br>
The simple fact is, that even though Verant has denounced character sales, they don't really have a problem with them, as long as the buyers and sellers leave them out of their squabbles. The account continues to generate money as long as it's subscribed. Pure and simple. The rest is just hullabaloo.<br>
******************************************<br>
<br>
To elaborate: I dont care for RP'ers. They slow the game down. I am and have always been a power gamer.<br>
I had a problem with cheaters from day one on this server. None of my memories are what you call 'pleasant'.<br>
Transposing 'now' with 'then' would mean very little to me.<br>
<br>
My primary beef is that people I dont like get away with it. That makes it bad in my book. Because I dont want them to get away with it. Very simple reasoning really.<br>
<br>
I am one of those idealistic fools that believe that everyone should start EQUAL and endure the same hardships. Otherwise you degrade the status of the people that ARE honest. I hold you Mr. Bodie in complete contempt. You are a prime mover in that process.<br>
People that sell you accounts are greedy selfish fools who never really cared about the game to begin with.<br>
Not people to be admired.<br>
