      After a explaining a few things to him and recieving a few more questions it became obvious he had switched out his account..(I thought perhaps he was foreign and didn't understand English/EQ slang well.) My curiousity peaked and I asked him if he was new to the game...to which he replied the obvious...I proceeded to question him and found out the he had bought the account from a guy in RL who was selling it in the Classified ads....all he did was switch from credit card to EQ Game Cards 2 months prior to selling the account (apparently..)<br>
      I don't know about any of you....but it took me a good while to learn my class...not only to learn it..but to RELEARN it as I leveled and got different gear.... I'm not sure I'd want to be the group harboring the n00bie 54th SK...just my opinion.<br>
      Leveling is a timesink...probably..I think I could agree w/ that...however..what purpose would the game serve if we were all &quot;born&quot; as strong as we possibly could be? IMHO....I think a game like that would be boring...maybe that's a good idea for VI to earn more cash......perhaps an EQ II Legends server w/ uber arse gear and everyone starts at lvl 65? /shrug.....sounds boring to me...I may hate the time it takes to level..but for some reason I continue to try.....they must be doing something right! <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START 8) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/glasses.gif ALT="8)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#575757><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub4.ezboard.com/bemarr.showUserPublicProfile?gid=kerrolthefury>Kerrol The Fury</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Smartass™</span><br>  Posts: 777<br> <font color=#E9D756>(10/31/02 11:07:17 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub4.ezboard.com/femarrdragonsandplanes.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=3766.topic&index=31>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: re: Mr Bodie</span><hr size=1> <!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><strong><em>Quote:</em></strong><hr>If it takes you three years to level a char to 65....somethings wrong 8-) <hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
